<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="no-matter-where-who-whatetc">no matter where, who, what,etc.</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>不论……；不管……</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You and I will always be friends, no matter what happens.
不管发生什么，你我永远是朋友。</p><footer>外研⑧ – 7</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>No matter how hard the rain falls and the wind blows, the police keep to their posts.
无论雨多急、风多大，警察一直坚守在自己的岗位上。</p></div></div>